OL,3,CDoubts over Iran-US talks as ceasefire
OL,4,Cdue to expire
OL,6,FThere are doubts over talks between
OL,7,FIran and the US, with Donald Trump
OL,8,Fgiving mixed messages about his
OL,9,Fcountry's next steps.
OL,11,FThe US president suggested he would
OL,12,Fstill be sending his negotiating team,
OL,13,Fled by Vice President JD Vance, to
OL,14,FPakistan's capital for talks on
OL,15,FWednesday, even though Iran has
OL,16,Finsisted it would not participate in
OL,17,Fdiscussions until Trump dialled back
OL,18,Fhis demands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
