OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776856004
OL,3,CDoubts over Iran-US talks as ceasefire
OL,4,Cdue to expire
OL,6,FTrump has said he's "highly unlikely"
OL,7,Fto renew the ceasefire before it
OL,8,Fexpires on Wednesday.
OL,10,FMohammed Bagher Qalibaf, Iran's chief
OL,11,Fnegotiator and parliament speaker,
OL,12,Fwrote on X early on Tuesday: "We do
OL,13,Fnot accept negotiations under the
OL,14,Fshadow of threats", and the Islamic
OL,15,FRepublic has been preparing "to reveal
OL,16,Fnew cards on the battlefield".
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
