OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776856004
OL,3,CDoubts over Iran-US talks as ceasefire
OL,4,Cdue to expire
OL,6,FOn Monday Trump denied he is under
OL,7,Fpressure to make a deal with Iran.
OL,9,FIn a series of posts on Truth Social,
OL,10,FTrump said he was "properly and
OL,11,Fjudiciously" using the US military to
OL,12,F"solve problems left to us by others
OL,13,Fof far less understanding or
OL,14,Fcompetence".
OL,16,F"I read the Fake News saying that I am
OL,17,Funder 'pressure' to make a Deal. THIS
OL,18,FIS NOT TRUE!" he wrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
