OL,3,CDoubts over Iran-US talks as ceasefire
OL,4,Cdue to expire
OL,6,FBritish Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,7,FCooper has described the current
OL,8,Fsituation as "a critical diplomatic
OL,9,Fmoment" as the end of a two-week US-
OL,10,FIran ceasefire looms.
OL,12,FSince the current conflict started,
OL,13,Ffighting has killed at least 3,375
OL,14,Fpeople in Iran and more than 2,290 in
OL,15,FLebanon.
OL,17,FA further 23 people have died in
OL,18,FIsrael and more than a dozen in Gulf
OL,19,FArab states, while 15 Israeli soldiers
OL,20,Fin Lebanon and 13 US service members
OL,21,Fthroughout the region have been killed.
